E_D("replace into `imicms_img` values('166','6','1457963911','知识','1','你的颈椎为什么有响声？','11','生活小常识','http://wx.eake.cn/uploads/2/257e21c8a9e1be8c/8/f/6/9/thumb_545b1b18a160f.png','1','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;background-color:#C3D69B;color:#3E3E3E;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;【更多你喜欢的】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;点击标题上面蓝色字“&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjYyNDU3MA==&amp;mid=201415213&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b22d138667085247c432f403f46815c5#rd&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;杰诚生活&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;”关注&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/BFobaMTWicLJBfrQc9bYXJhzib4zdTmIRsMwK6YtDqGmM4X3JtkCoZs8oH5xtGbx6IPFqFHENdMLqIPME8mtwuDQ/0&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一、脖子为什么一转就响？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		大\r\n家注意一个现象，小孩子，身体是软软的，绝对不会出现脖子响的问题。等我们上了一点岁数，一活动身体，就会出现关节响的情况，包括肩关节、膝关节，这个时\r\n候，我们就会说，唉，上了岁数了，都是老胳膊老腿了。什么是老胳膊老腿呢？其实，就是我们身体的气血供应不上，导致我们身体在变硬，关节在缺血的状态下干\r\n磨。我们脊椎的骨头和骨头之间，都会有椎间盘。那椎间盘到底有什么作用呢？椎间盘这个东西，里面80%都是水，越是年轻人,里面的水份含量就越高。等人老\r\n了，水分丢失了，椎间盘就收缩了，所以，人老了，身体就抽抽了，就是这个道理。其实这里指的水分，就是血 \r\n液。椎间盘的主要作用就是缓冲。比如我们跳起来打球落下的时候，地会对人体产生一个反作用力，如 \r\n果没有这个椎间盘，就成了骨头之间冲撞了，硬碰硬，硬碰硬会出现 \r\n什么情况大家可想而知。人怎么会受的了呢?\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/fneuMdl9tYLhT8vz2m8L64sbyBITQrDuwHZpduKnxT1zic1ulzqUjGQYnahCNwK7zN7jPcBWqLEXiarqXMlPbZjQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		另外，我们身体弯曲的时候，椎间盘的作用也是保护我们骨头之间在运动的时候不会受损。既然我们明白了这个道理，我 们就不难理解我们的脖子为什么一 \r\n转，里面的骨头就会嘎巴响了。给 大家举一个例子方便大家理解。 很多人一定骑过自行车。如果 我们的车轴里缺油了，会感觉怎么样？一定是骑着费劲，一定会感觉 \r\n里面的滚珠转动不灵活是不是，而 这种响动，有点类似我们的脖子 响，只不过，自行车轴转动靠的是 油，而我们骨头之间的转动靠的是 血。当我们血气双亏的时候，我们 \r\n的骨关节之间的椎间盘，没有充足的气血供应，会形成干磨的情况， 响动也就成自然了。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/fneuMdl9tYLhT8vz2m8L64sbyBITQrDuichdam3pU67G8ibTUtYcw6qrfibsjquk885gUD3DZh0UsPMnk1M2f2ic9Q/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;二、骨关节为何会病变？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		为什么骨关节特别是颈腰椎更容易发生病变呢？其实这里有很多 原因，主要有三点：更多养生资讯，请关注微信：but365\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/fneuMdl9tYLhT8vz2m8L64sbyBITQrDuXjMdjD2KQyz07U89zoVtrRKic3BUuwJhk4Uq5r6512neZKe32vBnfibQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1、是生理结构。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;我们注意 \r\n一个现象，就是我们的颈椎和腰 椎，特别容易出问题，但是胸椎却好得多。这是因为我们的胸椎周围 有肋骨牵拉保护着，形成了一种力 \r\n的相互作用，以确保我们的胸椎能够保持中正。但是，我们的颈椎和 腰椎则不然，它们没有肋骨牵拉固 \r\n定着，它们靠的是多组韧带和小肌肉群。如果这些组织发生问题，就会导致我们的颈腰椎出问题。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2、是工作姿势。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;当肌肉处 \r\n于紧张之中，时间长了就会形成乳 酸堆积，感觉肌肉酸痛。正常情况 下，如果胳膊腿酸了，我们活动一 下，很快就能解除这种乳酸堆积。 但是，用电脑就不一样了，由于我 \r\n们是长时间处于微弱的紧张状态， 这就好比温水煮青蛙一样，等我们 查觉的时候，就已经晚了。它造成的后果就是，我们颈腰椎周围的韧 带由于得不到充足的气血供应，就 \r\n会慢慢形成钙化，两侧的牵拉受力 开始不均匀，久而久之，椎间盘就 会突出，挤压周围的组织神经，我 们的颈腰椎病就会形成了。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3、是工作环境。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;如\r\n果再加上我们工作环境的寒和湿比较严重，比如，我们在地下室工作，比如我们在空调底下工作，都会造成环境中的寒和湿进入到体内，特别是对于那些气血本来就\r\n不够通畅的肌肉和韧带，形成潜在的影响，加重了我们病变部位的病情。第四，过食碳酸饮料。碳酸饮料会导致体内脱钙，久而久之，我们骨头变会得非常的疏松，\r\n那个时候，就不单纯是骨头响的问题了，而且还很容易导致骨折。这种情况，在西方的老年社会十分普遍。 \r\n因此，颈腰椎部位爱发病的原因，有生理结构的，有我们工作习惯的，有我们工作环境的，还有饮食的原因，总之，这些都是现代生活方式病的体现。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;三、如何解决一转就响？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		其实脖子响还好，如果你的膝关节再响，可就麻烦大了。你将手放在膝盖上，然后将脚离地，前后 \r\n摆动小腿，如果当你感觉膝关节里也有响动，那么就可以肯定地说，你现在全身已经是严重的气血双亏了。如果你摸不出来这种感觉，那好，你试试小孩子的膝盖，你再试试老年人的膝盖，对比一下，你就会有正确的感觉了。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/fneuMdl9tYLhT8vz2m8L64sbyBITQrDueFFR2q4xybia8VrDoUet45F9VcCOKx0OfPBNTGEkoybHzaXhbBXncSQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		为什么说膝盖响问题严重了 呢？因为在中医里，膝为筋之府， 而肝是主筋的，肝又是藏血的。只有当肝血不足的时候，才会导致上 述情况的发生。肝肾同源，肝血 \r\n亏，必然也是肾虚。这种人，如果 下楼梯、下山，当膝关节受力，需 要大量的血液供应的时候，血一定 供应不上，那样就会感觉膝盖两侧 痛，尤其是外侧痛。 \r\n病现于四肢五官，病存于五脏 六腑。那我们该如何调理也就清楚 了，送大家二十个字。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1、多多活动。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;尤其是天天 \r\n以电脑为伴的朋友，用一会儿电 脑，就要起来活动一下，同时活动 一下脖子，但千万不要做360度的 圆周运动，只作90度的向左转， \r\n向90度的向右转的动作，以确保我们脖子两侧的韧带都能够得到均衡 的牵拉。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2、远离空调。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;尤其是不要 \r\n让空调正对着吹。因为夏天人的汗毛孔是张着的，空调一吹，寒湿很 容易进入体内，会加重我们韧带的 钙化。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3、杜绝可乐。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;减少包括可乐在内的一切碳酸饮料的摄入，因为这种温水煮青蛙的过程是渐进 \r\n的，因此很难被人们重视。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4、补充营养。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;这里提到的营养，主要是指营养补充食品。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5、打通经络。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;这点最为重要。如果是脖子不舒服，最简单的方法就是穴位按摩，疏通经络。去美容养生馆一 \r\n天做一次即可，有条件的加上养生的药油产品效果更好。重点小肠经和膀胱经，如后溪，腕骨，昆仑，风池， 合谷。再结合气海，足三里补气补 \r\n血。以确保你的脖子是很软的，而不是很硬的。摸着是温暖的，而不是冰凉的。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#C00000;&quot;&gt;哪个女人是凶手？ 据说只有1%的人能看出来！&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:Simsun;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FFFF00;background-color:#7030A0;&quot;&gt;事件：&lt;/span&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		旅馆来了两对夫妇。其中一对是恩爱夫妇，另一对是杀夫外逃的通缉犯和其情夫。由于旅馆已收到通缉令，所以早有警惕。不巧，通缉照片不清楚，无法辩别哪一对是罪犯。但出门迎接的店老板一眼就看出了破绽，便知道哪一对是罪犯了。\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		那么你看出破绽了吗？\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;选A还是选B呢？&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/GqOVVGcjk47cvOnBJHMgxccvEye2S59MIfz73LBF6zLynlYhpBxGlg2HUCNMYPuwckC4g7FkoZO34siaaiaxLFjQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;安宁杰诚家政服务&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;联系电话：0871-68681294&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;strong&gt;移动电话：13888384509 15198862744&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','1415256916','1415256916','0','257e21c8a9e1be8c','你的颈椎为什么有响声？','','166','0','0','0',NULL,'1','1','0','1','','');");
E_D("replace into `imicms_img` values('165','6','1457963911','知识','1','云南方言笑话（j最新版）','11','生活小常识','http://wx.eake.cn/uploads/2/257e21c8a9e1be8c/9/2/b/7/thumb_545b1a702f519.jpg','1','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;background-color:#C3D69B;color:#3E3E3E;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;【更多你喜欢的】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;点击标题上面蓝色字“&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjYyNDU3MA==&amp;mid=201415213&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b22d138667085247c432f403f46815c5#rd&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;杰诚生活&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;”关注&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/BFobaMTWicLJBfrQc9bYXJhzib4zdTmIRsMwK6YtDqGmM4X3JtkCoZs8oH5xtGbx6IPFqFHENdMLqIPME8mtwuDQ/0&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;line-height:2em;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	1. \r\n曾经有一段相当板扎呢爱情摆的我前面，我就某克理皮，等到打失的才觉的相当闷灶，杂个会呢个鬼火，如果有机会再来一么我一定会对那个姑娘说：”老子爱你！“硬是要加个时间在前面呢话么干脆就来个一万年。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	2. 在哪个冷眯日眼呢冬天，我们抖鳞阔站呢站在脏巴拉施呢滇池边，我被你跟楞半倒呢外表吸引，特别是你曹逼十奈呢声音，从此每天想的都是憨眯日眼呢你！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	3. 卖苍蝇的故事\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	讲说是有一个狗呢突发其想逮了只蒼蝇装的火柴盒里面讲说是给它卖得,然后克得圆通山大喊&quot;卖藕吼啦,卖藕吼啦......&quot;么正喊的就有一个外地老表好奇,讲说是&quot;藕吼&quot;是那样东东从来某听说过就打算买来看看昆明呢新奇东东.经过讨价还价么就买了下来.么这个狗呢就挨这个老表讲啦&quot;等蛤么你打开盒盒看看就认得那样喊&quot;藕吼&quot;啦&quot;.等这个狗呢走得,老表就忙的打开想看看,那不知才一打开,该老表大喊到:&quot;藕吼,飞得啦.&quot;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	4. 屎壳郎与蚊子谈恋爱，郎：你喃样职业？蚊：护士，打针儿呢，你来？屎壳郎笑道：缘分啊，同行，我在中药局里首捏药丸．\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	5. 不准砸烟\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	某商店售货员对一个正在咂烟的顾客说：&quot;你皆，我们这点儿不准咂烟。&quot;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	顾客回答到：&quot;这个么是在你们这点儿买呢噻。&quot;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	售货员：&quot;莫挨我烦，我们这点儿还卖手纸呢！&quot;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	6. 云南人脖子嗓子不分,某生到北方上学,喉咙发炎,去校医室:医生，我脖子疼.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	医生围他脖子找了一圈,告诉他:你的脖子很好,不行就去医院照片.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	7. 整\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	有个外地人来云南，云南人问他：给有整掉了?\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	他：整是什么意思?\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：就是吃的意思\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	过一段时间他们去上厕所，厕所里有一大堆粪便\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：啊呀，这个要咋个整?\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	这个外地人当场就吐\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	8. 吃烤鸭\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	以前有个云南人,听说北京烤鸭很有名,所以一直想去吃.他来到北京,找到了北京烤鸭店,他坐在位子上对服务员说：&quot;拎一只烤鸭来甩甩(甩甩是吃的的意思)！&quot;服务员听了,马上去厨房拎了一只烤鸭,拿到云南人的面前甩了几下就走了,云南人以为他是拿去切,所以在那里干巴巴等了2个小时,他气愤不已,去找那个服务员的老板,并对他说：&quot;我点了一只烤鸭,怎么到现在还没有上菜(cai)?&quot;服务员很委屈地说：&quot;客人叫我拎一只烤鸭来甩甩,我就拎了一只在他面前甩了甩呀,我没错啊.&quot;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	9. 堵的毛冽儿\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	七十年代，一老外到昆明办事，住宾馆，一大早到北京路散步。突然，迎面跑来一匹毛驴，后有一官渡区农民气急败坏地追赶，边追边喊：“堵的毛冽儿，堵的毛冽儿！”......\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	老外心想：真不愧是礼仪之邦。于是热情迎上，并招呼：good morning,good \r\nmorning!并握住老农的手。老农使劲挣脱被拉住的手，边嚷：“叫你堵的毛冽儿，你堵的我整个哪样？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	10. \r\n玉溪人说乖和歪一样.一玉溪警察抓了一外地嫌犯,命令他&quot;歪歪&quot;站好,嫌犯连忙歪了身姿,警察见状大声呵斥:&quot;歪歪站好!&quot;嫌犯更是加剧身姿,警察上前踢了一脚,嫌犯困惑:警官,还不够歪吗?\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	11. 江川人叫鱼为日.一渔妇路边拦车:师傅,给我搭个车我给你日.司机急忙停车,扶她上去。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	12. 豌豆粉\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	一副市级领导陪外国友人游览金湖美景，到红炮台，在烧烤棚旁边，一老外面对美丽的金湖禁不住赞叹：wonderful!\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	该领导一听，转头对身边的工作人员说：给见着啦，我们个旧的豌豆粉还是有名气呢，连老外都认得啦，老外肯定想吃啦。接着对秘书下命令：快点克买豌豆粉，一人三碗！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	13. \r\n抗战期间，陈纳德呢小股飞虎队为了中国人民呢事业进驻开远帮中国人锤小日本，不懂事呢开远小蛙（小孩）一看到老美，就高声叫道：“洋老咪，我是你基爹。洋老咪，我是你基爹”，老美也不知说什么，还以为是对他们友好，就敲起大姆指用半生不熟的中国话连声道“顶好，顶好”！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	14. 有个老外来到个旧，说：“个旧人很热情，个旧女人的声音很好听象小猫叫一样”。问其故，问吃了饭了吗？答曰：“米有！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	15. 老外和个旧一个官员喝酒，这个官员帮老外倒酒，老外连说：“THANK YOU ，THANK \r\nYOU！”这个官员听了就说：“我们不新怎三口昵，要喝就一口哎特怎完，你怕是晓不得酿叫：感情深，一口闷......”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	16. \r\n丽江人说苹果听起来象屁股,某领到做报告:现在黄屁股不吃香了,外省的红屁股已占领了东南亚,我们一定要引进新品种,大力发展我们的优质红屁股.满堂焖笑.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	17.  在云南把“吃”念成“干”（Gàn），比如“吃饭”叫“干饭”；如果问人“你吃饱了没有”，要说“把肚子干大没有”。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	18.  还有口音差异，云南人很多分不清 an 和 \r\nang，比如上船和上床就分不清的，口音基本地道的导游就曾经闹了笑话（也许是故意的吧），他曾经说，来云南一定要经历3件事，上船（游洱海）、见雪（登玉龙雪山）、湿身（傣族泼水节目），不过由她口中婉娩道来，便是“上床、见血、失身”了。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	19. 爱昵族将男女之事称为擂,一村干部下山去接上级女干部,爬至半山,女干部坐下,边解衣服边喊:&quot;累 累 \r\n累&quot;村长连忙说:不擂不擂.女干部不悦:你不累我累.村长想上级发话不擂白不擂.就扑了上去。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	20. 傣族称哥哥为比，一络腮胡游客遇到个傣族少女,少女亲切的说:你嘴上的毛太象我的比了，游客哭笑不得,他不知少女的哥哥也是络腮胡。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	21. 瑶族说看和干,进和见都不清楚，一矮个瑶族男人看电影,前面的女孩老动,他忍无可忍大叫:姑娘,你屁股一动一动的,我干也干不进，举座哗然。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	22. 傣族管狗叫妈，当你听到什么吃不完喂妈，千万别误会。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	23.  傣族还管岁数、年代、大哥、大姐都叫比，文革时集会众人高呼~~~焖比,焖比,焖焖比(万岁,万岁,万万岁)!绝对虔诚， \r\n他叫你煮比煮比来玩我，是叫你年年来他家做客。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	24. \r\n在我们阿锅地方，有一个小伙子，名字叫做小二狗......有一天，小二狗开的他呢翻斗车进城，路上逗着个老奶要打车，小二狗就给他坐的翻斗车后面，一路上小二狗心情是板扎得很，哼点小曲就到城收了，小二狗忘记的老奶坐在后面，就跟车上呢东西倒得，一哈子才想起来，赶紧跑下去看，老奶看见小二狗就说，小伙子啊，太不好意思啦，我放了个屁就挨你呢车都震翻的。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	25. \r\n 老阴山顶的农家小吃真的有些名气了。这不，连刚到个旧几天的老外都慕名前来。并且老外事先已深入了解到：农家小吃也有城里人纯商业性的冒假的了黄灿灿的包谷饭，让人谗涎欲滴，老外走上前，验证一下：Are \r\nyou a farmer？小大坡村李小六：大哥，油倒还B有放，但是是“接日早星”才蒸出来呢，那呢会发霉？！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	26.  个旧市吉安街。一工人老师傅正在闲逛，过来一老外：Hello，Can you help me?\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	　　工人老师傅：你说西酿，我听不得懂！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	　　老外：Where are the GeJiu hotel?\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	　　别的没听明白，“GeJiu \r\nhotel”可是听的实实在在的，于是把老外引到永胜街一野药摊前，很有成就感地对老外说：之根就是猴头了，不过给是个旧的我也拿不实在！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	　　老外：！￥%……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	27. \r\n 在一个漆黑的夜里，一个人赶夜路，途经一片坟地。微风吹过，周围声音簌簌，直叫人汗毛倒竖，头皮发乍。就在这时，他忽然发现远处有一点红色的火光时隐时现。他首先想到的就是“鬼火”。于是，他战战兢兢地拣起一块石头，朝亮光扔去。只见那火光飘飘悠悠地飞到了另一个坟头的后面。他更害怕了，又拣起一块石头朝火光扔了过去，只见那亮光又向另一个坟头飞去。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	　　此时，他已经接近崩溃了。于是，又拣起了一块石头朝亮光扔去。这时，只听坟头后面传来了声音：“杂个说，是那个？整个大都不让人整痛快。烟都某咂完就三次了嘎！”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	28. 某男在戏院里横躺着占了四个位置，别人叫他起来，他只恩恩了两下不动地方。保安来了说：“小心我甩的起嘎，哪条道上呢？” &lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　他咬咬牙说：“楼上过道摔下来呢！”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	29. 云南东川话:“老子就天就站的制点,恨么你挝我嘛。毛看的你长得块,逗滋得老子拿大甲汗你!”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	30. 过年又逢春运，北京到昆明的火车上爆挤，有个中年妇女奋勇上车后突然大叫起来：“唉呀！我呢孩子不在得了......”列车员一听，忙上前询问，妈妈没了孩子，听着都让人难过。“您孩子多大的？”“三十七！” \r\n列车员满头雾水，上下打量，这女的看上去也就三十多点吧，为什么会有三十七岁的孩子，等眼光看到女人的脚上才明白过来，她是在找鞋子，三十七码的，被挤掉的。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	31. 巧家人很朴实热情，吃饭前洗手就谦让了一翻，客人说：“你先洗嘛”，巧家人当然不干，回答道：“咋个能主人先死（洗），你先死（洗）你先死（洗），你死（洗）了我再死（洗），一哈就死（洗）完了”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	32. 外省人和云南人呢对话\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：你是云南的？\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：YES\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：哇…好远啊……\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：（沉默中……）\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“云南解放没有？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“没有，我们上课的时候都带着枪”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“你原来会说汉语～！”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“恩，来的时候在火车上刚学的。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：   你们住窑洞吗？\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：   不，我们住深山。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“云南是不是在昆明？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“恩，云南是昆明的省会。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“你的很多小辫子呢？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“为了上大学只好剪掉了！”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“你们还吃生肉吗？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“我们老大发明了燧木取火，我们吃烧烤。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“你是云南人啊？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“是啊。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“那你们怎么来上学？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“骑驴到北京后坐飞机。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“那一定很久才到吧？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“习惯了，提前半年出发就行！\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：………\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“怎么不骑马呢？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“在云南，骑马都是穷人干的事情，像我们考出来的，都是骑骆驼和大象的。云南没有高考，考试都是比赛射箭，一公里以外摆个牌子，写上‘清华’，旁边放一个‘北大’，然后一个人有三次机会。我第一次射清华，第二次射北大，都失败了。我就射了最后一个牌子“复旦” \r\n。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“哦，这样啊，你很有才。。。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：呵呵，其实我也没那么好，只是随便考个‘复旦’而已。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“你们少数民族结婚是一夫一妻制吗？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“不是的，我们每个男人都可以娶10个老婆。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“不是吧~~~那你现在有几个老婆？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“我现在有12个老婆，等毕业后娶3个。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：吓死了！12个还不够多啊？怎么还要再娶3个，你不是说每个男人只能娶10个吗？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“10个不算多，我想娶几个就娶几个，因为我爸就是村长！”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“你们那边过清明用去烈士墓上香吗？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“我们这边没有烈士墓，我只去上香祀祖。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“那你们祀祖时也是烧纸钱和放鞭炮是吗？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“不是的，我们都是烧美元的，也不放鞭炮，我们都是往山下扔手榴弹的！”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	外省人：“云南有电话了吗？”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	云南人：“云南没有电话，我们都用手机。”\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size:16px;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#444444;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;关注我们提供更多省钱攻略，有惊喜特价，温馨提示，各种当地服务！&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size:16px;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 华文细黑, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#444444;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;如何尽快找到我们呢？亲！&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;backg